general.gigTitle: do shopify website development, designing, customization, and bug fixing

sellerCard.oneLiner: Please Contact Before Placing An Order!
sellerCard.description: I am Wabeez Khuram, a professional Shopify Store Developer and have worked for many clients all over the world with my expertise in JavaScript, JQuery, LIQUID, HTML & CSS. Now i am here to share my experience. I always believe that not quantity but quality is King in freelancing. I will 'NOT' stop tweaking unless you say WOW. Request me custom offer and i will give you the best.

description.content:
If you are looking for a Shopify store developer with skills like HTML5, CSS3, Liquid, JavaScript, jQuery for custom customization of your shopify website or want any specific page or any custom section and you need any help related to the bugs messing with your shopify store, then your are reading the gig of such an expert which can do any or all these tasks for you.


I am fully available to work on:


Complete Custom Theme: Fully custom shopify theme development as per your design or reference, with theme source code. No matter if you have the design on figam, PSD, XD, or in your mind.


Custom Sections or Pages Design: Develop a Custom Landing page, collection page, Product page, or any specific section as per your design and functionality.


Redesign a Shopify Store: Already have a shopfiy store and want to modify or completely new look for your Shopify store without messing up with your live store.


Bug fixation: Facing any trouble with the bugs in your Shopify stores and wanting them to be fixed, I will fix any type of Bug, Error, Code fix, Liquid Code, Javascript Issue.


Need any help or have incredible project, Ping me and i will get back to ASAP.

reviews.comment: Wabeez Khuram truly exceeded expectations! His code expertise and professionalism resulted in outstanding web pages. Delivery was prompt, communication smooth, and he went above and beyond. Always the best helping hands .

Wabeez is the best. When I need a pair of helping hands with Shopify I always look to him first. He is fast and always reliable. I look forward to working on more projects with him in the near future.

Wabeez Khuram delivered an exceptionally professional website development project. His language fluency, quick responsiveness, and politeness made the collaboration smooth and efficient. Highly recommend working with him!

This is the nth time working with Wabeez, and he never disappoints! His communication is always excellent, and he understands every task perfectly, making the entire process smooth and stress-free. The project was completed efficiently and with great attention to detail. Highly recommend him and will definitely work with him again in the future!

Wabeez did an outstanding job! He was very attentive to our instructions, ensured the project was completed on time, and kept great communication throughout the process. His expertise and professionalism were evident, making the entire experience smooth and efficient. We truly appreciate his attention to detail and dedication, and we would definitely work with him again in the future. Highly recommended!
